      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs super smoothly and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. It's the perfect companion for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it's going to make its next owner very happy. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
