    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit, equipped with eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio, delivers linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain consists of a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox and a GKN-sourced variable M-differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a five-link rear suspension and aluminum subframes. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization of the VANOS system and the integrity of the EDC (Electronic Damping Control) dampers make this a prime candidate for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
