    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean, featuring supple upholstery and fully functional technology. Mechanically, it is sound, having undergone regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance to ensure a smooth, confident, and reliable driving experience. It strikes the perfect balance for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that looks and drives beautifully.",
